    "Within this space, the city's perpetual motion feels as distant as the stars, despite its proximity." /
    "Some visitors take to the waters with serene boat rides that skirt the perimeter of the garden, their reflections trailing in the gentle wake. But it is the Nakajima-no-Ochaya teahouse that beckons us closer." /
